## 10. CI / Deployment Template

### GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/verify.yml`)

```yaml
name: Reliability Gate
on: [push, pull_request]
jobs:
  verify:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Backend Static Analysis
        run: |
          pip install mypy ruff pip-audit
          mypy . --strict
          ruff check .
          pip-audit
      - name: Frontend Static Analysis
        run: |
          npm install
          npm run lint
          npm run type-check
          npm audit --audit-level=high
      - name: Tests
        run: |
          pytest tests/ -x --tb=short
          npx playwright test
      - name: Anti-Pattern Gate
        run: |
          ! rg "MAX\(id" ./app
          ! rg "StaticPool" ./app
          ! rg "allow_origins=\[.\*.\]" ./app
```
